casebody.data:
Wednesday, May 6, 1998

MOTION DOCKET

97-1394. Akl v. El Chafehi.

Lucas App. No. L-96-129. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from' the Court of Appeals for Lucas County. Upon consideration of appellee’s motion to schedule oral argument at 9:00 a.m.,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that this be the second case called for oral argument Tuesday, May 26,1998.
